comments: Green (GSW) swipes down and initiates illegal contact with Okongwu's (ATL) wrist, which affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Murray (ATL) and Podziemski (GSW) come together as Murray defends the potential dribble hand-off, and marginal body contact occurs.
Bogdanovic (ATL) lands to the side of Curry (GSW) after legally contesting the jump shot attempt. Any contact that occurs with Curry's outwardly extended left leg is incidental.
Green (GSW) avoids making contact to the ball with his leg as he deflects the pass with his left hand.
Kuminga (GSW) extends his arm and reaches across Young's (ATL) path when contact occurs that affects Young's SQBR.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Green (GSW) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Quinones (GSW) has his arms extended forward in front of Young (ATL) off-ball when they come together briefly as Young leans into Quinones' chest.
Green (GSW) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Green (GSW) extends his arm toward the ball when marginal contact occurs with Johnson's (ATL) off-arm at the start of his dribble, which he can move through.
As Curry (GSW) attempts to split the defenders following the pick, marginal lower-body contact occurs from Murray (ATL), which Curry can move through.
Murray (ATL) contests the driving shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Curry's (GSW) arm after the release.
Thompson (GSW) is firming up in Murray's (ATL) path when marginal contact occurs as they briefly engage and separate during the screen.
Johnson (ATL) extends his left arm outward to contest and avoids making any arm contact with Curry (GSW) during Curry's driving shot attempt.
